snippet.title: SWPP - S01 Ep13 - Amber B
snippet.description:
Steve Walter Photo Podcast - Season 01 Everything is Art - Episode 12

I sit down with ameatuear model Amber Beauvillier. She’s French Canadian and how people sometimes talk differently. We discuss the Marvel Cinematic Universe and how excited we are for the films. We talk about what it means to be an “Instagram Model” and how to maintain relationships in the photo and modeling world. We talk about GWCs and how they’re effecting the photography and modeling community. We also talk about how I drink a lot of coffee and not enough water.
